(69, 2, '2019-08-26 11:00:55', '2019-08-26 15:00:55', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Learn more about all of the benefits included in your free Skipta community membership. Watch this video on how to easily navigate your community home stream and start connecting with your peers.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:core-embed/youtube {\"url\":\"https://youtu.be/p7Iza9hiGJA\",\"type\":\"video\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"youtube\",\"className\":\"wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-youtube wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\nhttps://youtu.be/p7Iza9hiGJA\n</div></figure>\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Find your community at&nbsp;<a href=\"https://skipta.com/communities\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ga-post-getting-the-most-communities-1\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Skipta.com (opens in a new tab)\">Skipta.com</a>. Once you’re registered, use the Home stream to share your own clinical case or updates for other medical professionals in your field to share, follow, like, and comment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Next, head over to the Curbside Consult tab where you can consult with colleagues in real-time on challenging patient cases. Create your own Curbside Consult to gain insight from your peers on a puzzling case. You can also browse through an overview of Curbside Consult’s to add your own expertise on a variety of topics; share your opinions and experiences in the comment section and follow the case for further updates.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Explore the Showcase tab which allows members to engage with content and resources created by some of the leading professional organizations and universities.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In the News tab, you can stay up-to-date with the top articles and updates relevant to your community.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Think you can get the top score? Go to the Compete tab to access clinical games and medical challenges where you can demonstrate your knowledge and compete against your peers.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Time for a fresh start? Skipta’s Careers feature allows members to search for their next job opportunity. Narrow down your preferences and apply directly from the recruiter’s site.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://skipta.com/blog/what-is-a-focus-area/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ga-post-getting-the-most-focus-area\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Focus Are (opens in a new tab)\">Focus Area</a>&nbsp;tab, you will find a dedicated area for information, resources, and cross-specialty collaboration specific to your specialized concentration. You can access relevant content, challenging cases, and cross-collaboration with verified physicians throughout multiple Skipta communities.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Interested in learning more about Skipta and all of its community features? Check out our&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"FAQ page (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://skipta.com/faqs/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ga-post-getting-the-most-faqs\">FAQ page</a>&nbsp;for more information. And don’t forget to subscribe to our&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCC4Js4kCU2BKOYxeCoKQo8w\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ga-post-getting-the-most-youtube\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Youtube channel (opens in a new tab)\">Youtube channel</a>&nbsp;for the latest videos related to Skipta and all of its communities!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://skipta.com/communities\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ga-post-getting-the-most-communities-2\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Find Your Community Today (opens in a new tab)\">Find Your Community Today</a></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Getting the Most Out of Your Skipta Community Membership', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'getting-the-most-out-of-your-skipta-community-membership', '', '', '2019-09-28 17:11:11', '2019-09-28 21:11:11', '', 0, 'https://sandbox.skipta.com/?p=69', 0, 'post', '', 0),
